msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: sect2/para
#: xml/smt_certificates.xml:232
msgid "The synchronization of time between the SMT server and clients is highly recommended. Each server certificate has a validity period. If the client happens to be set to a time outside of this period, the certificate validation on the client side fails."
